ata and public online\ndata harvested from IMDb, Rotten Tomatoes, and Google to prescribe operational\ndecisions that outperform baseline measures. Specifically, the data we collect,\nleveraged by our methods, accounts for an 88\\% improvement as measured by our\nP.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Feb 2014 05:10:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Jun 2014 17:25:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 9 Feb 2015 20:07:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2018 15:36:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-20"}
